			<p align="center"><span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;"><a class="logo-anchor" href="https://3fxyvvmr.r.us-east-1.awstrack.me/L0/https:%2F%2Fwww.taskade.com/1/0100019379ccdb34-7e6c39a9-a1ad-41aa-a450-c412f1168c28-000000/0U9f3aW0stwQ4iKVdd_Hwef5nSw=402" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-decoration: underline; color: #ff2d60; display: block;"><img class="left" src="https://www.taskade.com/newsletters/uploads/1666116818.png" style="border: 0px; outline: none; text-decoration: none; width: 42px; height: 42px;" /></a></span></p>

			<p><span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;">Hi there&nbsp; 🐑</span></p>

			<p><span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;">Transform your projects with&nbsp;Project Views &mdash; your productivity Origami! 🦩 Like shaping paper into art, fold your&nbsp;project into multiple forms without altering its core.</span></p>

			<p>&nbsp;</p>

			<h1 class="table-card-td-body-p-title">✍️ List / Outline View</h1>

			<p><span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;">Perfect for tasks, agendas, and note-taking. Ideal when you want to work from top to bottom, capturing ideas quickly. 👉 Use Case: Great for meeting agendas, daily to-do lists, and brainstorming sessions.&nbsp;<a href="https://3fxyvvmr.r.us-east-1.awstrack.me/L0/https:%2F%2Fhelp.taskade.com%2Fhc%2Fen-us%2Farticles%2F12757582963091/1/0100019379ccdb34-7e6c39a9-a1ad-41aa-a450-c412f1168c28-000000/3n1Pr3fZsxzuVEtbEFFZqrW0TJY=402" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-decoration: none; color: #ff2d60;">Learn more</a>.</span></p>

			<p><span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;"><img alt="Taskade AI" src="https://www.taskade.com/newsletters/uploads/1698689136.png" style="border: 0px; border-radius: 20px; outline: none; text-decoration: none; max-width: 695px; width: 100%;" /></span></p>

			<h1 class="table-card-td-body-p-title">&nbsp;</h1>

			<p>&nbsp;</p>

			<h1 class="table-card-td-body-p-title">📋&nbsp;Board / Kanban View</h1>

			<p>Visualize tasks in columns, making it easy to manage project phases or categories. 👉 Use Case: Ideal for&nbsp;development sprints, content calendars, and workflow management.&nbsp;<span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;"><a href="https://3fxyvvmr.r.us-east-1.awstrack.me/L0/https:%2F%2Fhelp.taskade.com%2Fhc%2Fen-us%2Farticles%2F10460110476179/1/0100019379ccdb34-7e6c39a9-a1ad-41aa-a450-c412f1168c28-000000/VClZpqWEFl4HaP2j7b6k-R4c84c=402" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-decoration: none; color: #ff2d60;">Learn more</a></span>.</p>

			<p><span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;"><img alt="Taskade AI Research" src="https://www.taskade.com/newsletters/uploads/1698689170.gif" style="border: 0px; border-radius: 20px; outline: none; text-decoration: none; max-width: 695px; width: 100%;" /></span></p>

			<h1 class="table-card-td-body-p-title">&nbsp;</h1>

			<h1 class="table-card-td-body-p-title">&nbsp;</h1>

			<h1 class="table-card-td-body-p-title">🗓&nbsp;Calendar View</h1>

			<p>See tasks and deadlines in a calendar layout, and visualize upcoming tasks due for any project. 👉 Use Case: Perfect for managing deadlines, scheduling meetings, and tracking milestones.&nbsp;<span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;"><a href="https://3fxyvvmr.r.us-east-1.awstrack.me/L0/https:%2F%2Fhelp.taskade.com%2Fhc%2Fen-us%2Farticles%2F5260144580499/1/0100019379ccdb34-7e6c39a9-a1ad-41aa-a450-c412f1168c28-000000/BwvLKJIR8Vqx_lBd4tWhf9ma-og=402" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-decoration: none; color: #ff2d60;">Learn more</a>.</span></p>

			<p><span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;"><img alt="Taskade AI Research" src="https://www.taskade.com/newsletters/uploads/1698689145.png" style="border: 0px; border-radius: 20px; outline: none; text-decoration: none; max-width: 695px; width: 100%;" /></span></p>

			<p>&nbsp;</p>

			<h1 class="table-card-td-body-p-title">📊&nbsp;Action View</h1>

			<p>Display tasks in a table with customizable columns. 👉 Use Case: Best for tracking project status, assigning tasks, and customer relationship management.&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;"><a href="https://3fxyvvmr.r.us-east-1.awstrack.me/L0/https:%2F%2Fhelp.taskade.com%2Fhc%2Fen-us%2Farticles%2F10488503329683/1/0100019379ccdb34-7e6c39a9-a1ad-41aa-a450-c412f1168c28-000000/1Me6JBLvL3jgF0CJDstEZc4GrVI=402" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-decoration: none; color: #ff2d60;">Learn more</a>.</span></p>

			<p><span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;"><img alt="Taskade AI Research" src="https://www.taskade.com/newsletters/uploads/1698689252.png" style="border: 0px; border-radius: 20px; outline: none; text-decoration: none; max-width: 695px; width: 100%;" /></span></p>

			<h1 class="table-card-td-body-p-title">&nbsp;</h1>

			<h1 class="table-card-td-body-p-title">🧠&nbsp;Mind Map View</h1>

			<p>Visualize complex ideas, projects, and workflows. 👉 Use Case: Excellent for brainstorming sessions, flowcharts, and project planning.&nbsp;<span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;"><a href="https://3fxyvvmr.r.us-east-1.awstrack.me/L0/https:%2F%2Fhelp.taskade.com%2Fhc%2Fen-us%2Farticles%2F12757664773139/1/0100019379ccdb34-7e6c39a9-a1ad-41aa-a450-c412f1168c28-000000/bkYDve9kuKnsAFpoGlnJYeZhOIk=402" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-decoration: none; color: #ff2d60;">Learn more</a>.</span></p>

			<p><span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;"><img alt="Taskade AI Research" src="https://www.taskade.com/newsletters/uploads/1698689185.png" style="border: 0px; border-radius: 20px; outline: none; text-decoration: none; max-width: 695px; width: 100%;" /></span></p>

			<p>&nbsp;</p>

			<h1 class="table-card-td-body-p-title">▲ Organizational Chart View</h1>

			<p>Visualize your project or team in a hierarchical structure to see the bigger picture. 👉 Use Case: Team onboarding, departmental planning, workflow optimization, and stakeholder mapping.&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;"><a href="https://3fxyvvmr.r.us-east-1.awstrack.me/L0/https:%2F%2Fhelp.taskade.com%2Fhc%2Fen-us%2Farticles%2F12757682226963/1/0100019379ccdb34-7e6c39a9-a1ad-41aa-a450-c412f1168c28-000000/6ljS3X8cuZcb8jB26cgr0AvZFgM=402" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-decoration: none; color: #ff2d60;">Learn more</a>.</span></p>

			<p><span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;"><img alt="Taskade AI Research" src="https://www.taskade.com/newsletters/uploads/1698689224.gif" style="border: 0px; border-radius: 20px; outline: none; text-decoration: none; max-width: 695px; width: 100%;" /></span></p>

